org.terrier.evaluation.Evaluation

Packages that use Evaluation
org.terrier.evaluation Provides an interface and the classes to process relevance assessments and perform standard evaluation of retrieval results. 
 

Uses of Evaluation in org.terrier.evaluation
 

Subclasses of Evaluation in org.terrier.evaluation
 class AdhocEvaluation
          Performs the evaluation for TREC's tasks, except the named page task.
 class AdhocFullQueryEvaluation
          Performs a query by query evaluation of a results file.
 class NamedPageEvaluation
          Performs the evaluation for TREC's named/home page finding task.
